        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Mentoring to Succeed Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to award grants to entities such as educational agencies, schools, and local governments to establish, expand, or support school-based mentoring programs that assist at-risk students in developing cognitive skills and promoting social-emotional learning to prepare them for success in high school, postsecondary education, and the workforce.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
